    </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 t\u1edbi kh\u00e1m \u1edf 3 b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n l\u1edbn, Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau h\u01a1n 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00ean b\u00e0n m\u1ed5 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i dai d\u1eb3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh chia s\u1ebb th\u00ec ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 30 ph\u00fat.Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0110o\u00e0n Nguy\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c y b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lee Dong Jun v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00e0ng Nh\u00f4\u201d, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang facebook c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed7 xong \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, Tu\u1ea5n Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 6 th\u00e1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\nRoboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1055","checkdouble":"184036"},{"date":"16:24 11/04","title":"V\u1eeba \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Roma ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em tin bu\u1ed3n cho... Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/vua-de-bep-barca-nguoi-roma-tiep-tuc-dem-tin-buon-cho-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}