ec3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" title=\"Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/vua-de-bep-barca-nguoi-roma-tiep-tuc-dem-tin-buon-cho-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch James Pallotta cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao Alisson l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ch\u1ee9? C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kia m\u00e0. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Alisson, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson n\u0103m nay 24 tu\u1ed5i, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stadio Olimpico. \u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Ederson Moraes &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League nh\u01b0 Roma &ndash; v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Loris Karius. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Alisson v\u00e0 Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, sau khi h\u1ecd m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mohamed Salah khi c\u0169ng b\u00e1n cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca-184-184014.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca-184-184014.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Barca...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league-184-184010.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league-184-184010.html\">Thua \u0111au Liverpool, Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League sau khi Man City b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ea5t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sane \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Liverpool, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1054","checkdouble":"184025"},{"date":"17:13 11/04","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City ch\u1ec9 ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-sau-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin: