,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Liverpool t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a Leroy Sane. V\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City \u1ea5m \u1ee9c v\u00ec pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Sane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool</strong></span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Antonio Mateu l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. Pha quay ch\u1eadm cho th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a James Milner v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Man City \u0111ang d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf thua 0-3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, HLV Pep Guardiola c\u1ee7a Man City t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Mateu. Sau hi\u1ec7p 1, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb \u201cVua \u00e1o \u0111en\u201d \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i theo d\u00f5i ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gabriel Jesus phat bieu sau tran Man City vs Liverpool ve Sane hinh anh\" title=\"Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool v\u1ec1 Sane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-sau-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Sane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. Chung cu\u1ed9c, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-man-city-vs-liverpool-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183965.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City c\u1ee7a anh th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool 1-2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</strong></span> v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng th\u1eadt ch\u1eafc. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi Sane, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 sau. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f4i khi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn x\u1ea3y ra.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league-184-184010.html\">Thua \u0111au Liverpool, Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi-184-184005.html\">Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-da-danh-bai-doi-bong-manh-nhat-the-gioi-184-184004.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-bai-ca-man-city-lovren-van-e-so-1-doi-thu-o-ban-ket-c1-184-184003.html\">H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Man City, Lovren v\u1eabn e s\u1ee3 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gabriel-jesus-man-city-da-khoi-dau-tot-nhung-184-183996.html\">Gabriel Jesus: Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-man-city-12-liverpool-184-183991.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1053","checkdouble":"184035"},{"date":"17:20 11/04","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool.png",