ntal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Man City \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mohamed Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span>, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 nguoi thang va 4 nguoi thua sau tran Man City vs Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/3-nguoi-thang-va-4-nguoi-thua-sau-tran-Man-City-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPh\u00fat 56, Ederson c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mane, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Salah, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp Man City c\u1ea7n ghi 4 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa trong h\u01a1n 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m 39 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. 180 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, Salah d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Kevin De Bruyne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Man City (147 l\u1ea7n). Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, anh c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne dut diem nhieu nhung khong hieu qua\" title=\"De Bruyne d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/de-bruyne.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 song s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 De Bruyne mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn. Anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Salah.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Kop ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec De Bruyne d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 5 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c De Bruyne th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ecf ra n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn Man City l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jurgen Klopp</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trent Alexander-Arnold, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, b\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Andrew Robertson c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Georginio Wijnaldum, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vai tr\u00f2 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7&hellip;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp dang bien Liverpool thanh tap the kho bi danh bai\" title=\"Klopp \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn Liverpool th\u00e0nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn Liverpool th\u00e0nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u00e3 linh ho\u1ea1t trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a The Kop v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn Liverpool th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ghi 33 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 10, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U (12). C\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad. Virgil Van Dijk b\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 Raheem Sterling c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Gabriel Jesus ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung trung ve cua hai doi co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/trung-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Man City uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAymeric Laporte th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Sadio Mane. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 c\u1ee7a Salah, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 Mane v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ghi b\u00e0n. Nicolas Otamendi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 Roberto Firmino v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Roberto Firmino</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng: D\u00f9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 80 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng Roberto Firmino l\u1ea1i ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 52 l\u1ea7n, \u00edt h\u01a1n 7 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi Mane, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino ghi ban cho Liverpool\" title=\"Firmino ghi ban cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Firmino c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 8 \u1edf Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Firmino \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n, anh l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, t\u1eeb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFirmino c\u0169ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a Firmino \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Salah.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Pep Guardiola</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, Pep c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola gay that vong rat lon\" title=\"Pep Guardiola g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m 2015 khi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich th\u00ec Pep Guardiola m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep \u0111\u00e3 7 l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jurgen Klopp, kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ef1u HLV Barca nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 68%. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, song ch\u00ednh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n khi\u1ebfn Man xanh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sane ko duoc cong nhan ban thang\" title=\"Sane ko duoc cong nhan ban thang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-sau-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man City c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Man City \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 20 l\u1ea7n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 3 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (Theo&nbsp;squawka.com)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1052","checkdouble":"184038"},{"date":"17:22 11/04","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Real vs Juve: L\u1ea5y Barca l\u00e0m b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/truoc-tran-real-vs-juve-lay-barca-lam-bai-hoc.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWeb