</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/luke-shaw-da-den-luc-roi-khoi-dia-nguc-old-trafford-172-182489.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi M.U </strong></span>\u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Ryan Bertrand thay Luke Shaw hinh anh\" title=\"MU mua Ryan Bertrand thay Luke Shaw h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/MU-mua-Ryan-Bertrand-thay-Luke-Shaw-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Luke Shaw, Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAshley Young \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho mua s\u1eafm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Southampton</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo The Sun, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Bertrand c\u1ee7a Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bertrand duoc cham diem cao nhat ben phia Southampton\" title=\"Bertrand \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/mu-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Ryan Bertrand \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Bertrand lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Southampton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Bertrand, Man City c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. \u0110\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Bertrand mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Southampton v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Southampton, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham. Spurs h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Man \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bertrand \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/20756-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bertrand \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1049","checkdouble":"184042"},{"date":"14:42 11/04","title":"Fan West Ham n\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/fan-west-ham-nem-do-choi-nguoi-lon-vao-khung-thanh-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight: