       </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Georgina Rodriguez l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. \u1ea2nh: NN.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Instagram, Georgina Rodriguez c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao l\u00e0ng showbiz x\u1ee9 b\u00f2 t\u00f3t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n, c\u00e1c fan, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi follow t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecdc m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ri\u00eang t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 v\u1edbi C. Ronaldo. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Georgina Rodriguez v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo g\u1eedi d\u00f2ng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quan \u0111i\u1ec3m. \"\u0110\u1ea7u \u00f3c lo toan cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n trong s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1i tim y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c\", b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i CR7 vi\u1ebft. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f4 c\u00f2n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u Georgina Rodriguez \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a c\u00f4 tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Tuy v\u1eady \u1edf hai l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau si\u00eau sao Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng anti-fan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1047","checkdouble":"184028"},{"date":"15:45 11/04","title":"Fan Man City \"m\u1ea5t v\u1ee3\" v\u00ec thua c\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn derby Manchester","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/fan-man-city-mat-vo-vi-thua-cuoc-tran-derby-manchester.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"1046","checkdouble":"184031"},{"date":"15:53 11/04","title":"Ronaldo t\u1eb7ng qu\u00e0 cho th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng MU","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/ronaldo-tang-qua-cho-than-dong-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-t