et-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 Suwon JS Cup, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e2n cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U19 Suwon JS Cup. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p hai n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 U19 Mexico v\u00e0 U19 Ma R\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10/2018 \u2013 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u2018ch\u1ea5m\u2019 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u01b0ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 SEA Games 30.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ve nuoc de tuyen quan cho U23 Viet Nam hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e2n cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-ve-nuoc-de-tuyen-quan-cho-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e2n cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd g\u00e1c l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Suwon JS Cup.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 v\u00e0 \u0110TQG Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i hi v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i U19 Suwon JS Cup s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18 t\u1edbi 24/4 t\u1edbi. Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n hai chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i U19 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u00e0 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1041","checkdouble":"184029"},{"date":"15:42 11/04","title":"T\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a PSG mu\u1ed1n \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Chelsea?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/19/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial